snippet.title: Diana and Toys from Goldfish
snippet.description:
Diana saw a Goldfish and asked her for new toys: play house and a toy car. Brother Roma also wanted toys and asked them from the Golden Fish. But when the children began to quarrel, Gold fish took all the toys back ... fun video for kids
